<HEADLINE>
<P>
BRIEFLY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Weyerhaeuser Co. is closing its milk carton plant in La Puente, resulting in 
the loss of 140 jobs during the next two to four months . . . A $23.3-million 
stock offering was launched to finance the purchase of the Mustang Ranch, east 
