<TEXT>
<P>
John F. (Jack) Walker Jr. has been named managing partner of the law firm 
Latham &amp; Watkins. He succeeds Clinton R. Stevenson, who has retired after 
serving as managing partner for 21 years. Walker most recently was a member of 
the firm's executive committee. Latham &amp; Watkins is headquartered in Los 
Angeles and has offices in Washington, Chicago, New York, Orange County and San 
Diego. 
