AGOURA SOCCER COACH TO RESIGN AFTER PLAYOFFS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Dave Godwin, the Agoura High girls' soccer coach who in five years led the 
Chargers to three consecutive Southern Section 2-A Division championships, 
announced his resignation Monday effective the end of the season. No 
replacement has been named. 
</P>
